product_name: Natural High Cheese Enchilada Ranchero - 2 Servings
long_description: Instant vegetarian blend of soft tortillas, mild seasoning, rice and aged cheddar cheese. To prepare, set aside cheese and mix remaining ingredients with boiling water in the pouch provided; let stand, then fold in cheese and serve. At higher altitudes cook in a pot, simmering three to four minutes.
